Package: bingbadaboom
Version: 1.084
Section: base
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python-yaml, python-psutil
Maintainer: Markus Bawidamann
Description: The BingBadaboom crash notifier. Let no crashes be forgotten, track them all! Shows the truth about system stability! The bingbadaboomd daemon runs in the background and collects runtime hours and crashes, while the bingbadaboom-util tool is to calculate statistics like Markus-index (stability index) and runtime statistics.







